Genetic Algorithms. 

Explanation: The paper discusses the application of Genetic Programming (a type of Genetic Algorithm) to chaotic time series prediction. It explores the dynamics of Genetic Programming and the importance of finding an optimal representation for the problem domain. The paper also proposes a modification to the crossover operator to improve search performance. While other sub-categories of AI may be relevant to the topic of time series prediction, the focus of this paper is on the use of Genetic Programming.
